{"type": "article", "id": 28052, "title": "多功能笔筒", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-12T06:57:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702151916LPWmJMH6SOjBdT4i.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>你在涂鸦的时候有没有因为拿橡皮或者卷笔刀而分心，错过了自己精彩的灵感？设计师 Andrew Pyza 设计的这款木质铅笔筒 pencil+ 是一个集多种功能为一体的设计，让你在创作时更少分心，并且将每一支铅笔都用到最短。它的两端分别安装了卷笔刀和金属套件，后者可以固定最短 14 毫米长的铅笔，或是圆柱状的橡皮。pencil+ 预计将会在 Kickstarter 上开展众筹，如果你对它感兴趣的话可以通过<a href=\"http://www.pencilplus.nl/#contact\">链接</a>获取最新消息。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151914ZhyMQY2uco6D4eWf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.419\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151915pbSAlViGz2YNKBoT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46518987\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151915Lt7wIE13uCTKoDv6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53024194\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702151916R5xTaMhG8NvtVszQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.35048544\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}